{
  "video_id": "7Q59suYxIec",
  "title": "How conscious investors can turn up the heat and make companies change | Vinay Shandal",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13470.0,
      "end_time": 16277.0,
      "text": "We love to engage on the issues of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16302.0,
      "end_time": 17460.0,
      "text": "We love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17484.0,
      "end_time": 18942.0,
      "text": "We comment on the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18966.0,
      "end_time": 21309.0,
      "text": "we post our views on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21333.0,
      "end_time": 24700.0,
      "text": "we march, we protest ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24950.0,
      "end_time": 27849.0,
      "text": "But who among us is working on solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27874.0,
      "end_time": 30334.0,
      "text": "big solutions to big issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30358.0,
      "end_time": 32270.0,
      "text": "like gun violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32293.0,
      "end_time": 34290.0,
      "text": "mistreatment of workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34530.0,
      "end_time": 35762.0,
      "text": "flood, famine, drought?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35786.0,
      "end_time": 38307.0,
      "text": "Who is on it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38331.0,
      "end_time": 39494.0,
      "text": "Boom!"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40781.0,
      "end_time": 42800.0,
      "text": "These guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42105.0,
      "end_time": 44117.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44142.0,
      "end_time": 46838.0,
      "text": "What? You were hoping for Peter Parker?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46862.0,
      "end_time": 48290.0,
      "text": "The Avengers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48314.0,
      "end_time": 51620.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t expect this beacon of diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51860.0,
      "end_time": 57400.0,
      "text": "these good-looking, nicely dressed dudes just oozing charisma to solve the issues?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57425.0,
      "end_time": 60575.0,
      "text": "Well good, because they&#39;re actually not going to solve the issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60600.0,
      "end_time": 63944.0,
      "text": "But before you dismiss them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63968.0,
      "end_time": 66368.0,
      "text": "let me say, they&#39;re not going to solve the issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66392.0,
      "end_time": 68616.0,
      "text": "but they will show us how."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69100.0,
      "end_time": 70842.0,
      "text": "So who are they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70866.0,
      "end_time": 72333.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re activist investors:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72950.0,
      "end_time": 78867.0,
      "text": "Carl Icahn, Dan Loeb, Paul Singer, Barry Rosenstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78891.0,
      "end_time": 82474.0,
      "text": "These are the modern-day OGs of Wall Street."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82498.0,
      "end_time": 83551.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83575.0,
      "end_time": 84737.0,
      "text": "These are scary dudes."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84761.0,
      "end_time": 86416.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean Green Goblin scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 88655.0,
      "text": "I mean real scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89169.0,
      "end_time": 93814.0,
      "text": "The fear they strike in the hearts of a company&#39;s CEO and board"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93838.0,
      "end_time": 95696.0,
      "text": "when they enter its stock"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95721.0,
      "end_time": 100575.0,
      "text": "is the same fear you feel when you hear a bear outside your tent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100599.0,
      "end_time": 101842.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s dark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101866.0,
      "end_time": 104398.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re sitting there with a mouthful of Doritos --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104422.0,
      "end_time": 105483.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 105507.0,
      "end_time": 106661.0,
      "text": "that just moments ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106685.0,
      "end_time": 109653.0,
      "text": "you had snuck out of the tent to pull down from the bear hang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109677.0,
      "end_time": 111750.0,
      "text": "because you had the munchies."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111990.0,
      "end_time": 112570.0,
      "text": "That fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113245.0,
      "end_time": 114963.0,
      "text": "And in that moment, you are praying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114987.0,
      "end_time": 118372.0,
      "text": "\"Oh Lord, please let this bear be passing through.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118397.0,
      "end_time": 121229.0,
      "text": "That bear is not passing through!"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121253.0,
      "end_time": 124170.0,
      "text": "That bear made a detour for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124410.0,
      "end_time": 126420.0,
      "text": "Bears like Doritos!"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126660.0,
      "end_time": 127198.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127222.0,
      "end_time": 129525.0,
      "text": "Activists like money."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129550.00000000001,
      "end_time": 135514.0,
      "text": "Some activists also like Doritos, but they definitely want money."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136313.0,
      "end_time": 140647.0,
      "text": "And the way they make money, the way they create value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 140671.0,
      "end_time": 143269.0,
      "text": "is by getting management of corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 143293.0,
      "end_time": 144909.0,
      "text": "to make changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 146500.0,
      "end_time": 149127.0,
      "text": "Now, some will argue that the changes they create,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 149151.0,
      "end_time": 151789.0,
      "text": "the value they create, is too short-term in nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152349.0,
      "end_time": 156106.0,
      "text": "And others will say the tactics they use are egregious."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156130.0,
      "end_time": 157543.0,
      "text": "I agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157568.0,
      "end_time": 159280.0,
      "text": "Long, drawn-out lawsuits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 159304.0,
      "end_time": 160788.0,
      "text": "public smear campaigns --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 160812.0,
      "end_time": 163152.0,
      "text": "there is no need for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 163741.0,
      "end_time": 166894.0,
      "text": "But I must say, there&#39;s a small handful of activists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 166918.0,
      "end_time": 168214.0,
      "text": "very small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 168238.0,
      "end_time": 171174.0,
      "text": "that go to great lengths to be constructive and collaborative."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 171198.0,
      "end_time": 173920.0,
      "text": "And overall, we have to give credit where credit is due."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 173944.0,
      "end_time": 177790.0,
      "text": "As a group, they have managed to catalyze large-scale change"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 177814.0,
      "end_time": 179350.0,
      "text": "in large corporations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 179590.0,
      "end_time": 181278.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s no small feat."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 183824.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 184888.0,
      "end_time": 187948.0,
      "text": "where all investors were working with management to make change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 187972.0,
      "end_time": 189816.0,
      "text": "not just to make more money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 190981.0,
      "end_time": 193924.0,
      "text": "but to improve the environment and society."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 193948.0,
      "end_time": 198612.0,
      "text": "Imagine what a greener and better world this would be."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198636.0,
      "end_time": 200588.0,
      "text": "Now, why? Why would an investor bother?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 200612.0,
      "end_time": 203536.0,
      "text": "And at first, blush I&#39;m with you: Why would an investor care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203560.0,
      "end_time": 205903.0,
      "text": "Because if doing well on ESG issues --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205927.0,
      "end_time": 208712.0,
      "text": "environmental, social and governance issues --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 208736.0,
      "end_time": 211400.0,
      "text": "was just an act of good corporate citizenship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212441.0,
      "end_time": 214350.0,
      "text": "then I agree, investors would not care."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214374.0,
      "end_time": 215817.0,
      "text": "But the good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 215841.0,
      "end_time": 219190.0,
      "text": "and perhaps the saving grace for our collective futures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219430.0,
      "end_time": 222757.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s so much more than an act of good corporate citizenship."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223376.0,
      "end_time": 224745.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s good business."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225383.0,
      "end_time": 228143.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s now enough evidence that shows a clear correlation"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228167.0,
      "end_time": 231373.0,
      "text": "between ESG performance and financial performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231397.0,
      "end_time": 234603.0,
      "text": "Companies that do good for the environment and society"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234628.0,
      "end_time": 236607.0,
      "text": "also do well financially."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237362.0,
      "end_time": 239807.0,
      "text": "And some of the best companies are catching on."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239831.0,
      "end_time": 241161.0,
      "text": "Like Adidas:"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241186.0,
      "end_time": 245108.0,
      "text": "Adidas is cleaning up the ocean and making money in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 245132.0,
      "end_time": 249332.0,
      "text": "Adidas teamed up with an organization called Parley for the Oceans."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249356.0,
      "end_time": 252893.0,
      "text": "Parley goes out and collects plastic waste from the ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 252917.0,
      "end_time": 255385.0,
      "text": "Adidas uses the plastic waste to make shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255409.0,
      "end_time": 258160.0,
      "text": "Shoes made with plastic from the ocean:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 258399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260770.99999999997,
      "text": "good for the environment and good for business."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 261209.0,
      "end_time": 265107.0,
      "text": "Because if you know that rapidly growing consumer segment known as hipsters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 265721.0,
      "end_time": 267363.0,
      "text": "and I know you know hipsters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 267387.0,
      "end_time": 271000.0,
      "text": "then you know that a hipster faced with the choice between a no-name shoe"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 271240.0,
      "end_time": 273310.0,
      "text": "and an Adidas made with plastic from the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 273334.0,
      "end_time": 277308.0,
      "text": "will pick the Adidas every day of the week and twice on Sunday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 277332.0,
      "end_time": 279745.0,
      "text": "and then walk around like it&#39;s no big deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 279769.0,
      "end_time": 282916.0,
      "text": "but look for every opportunity to talk about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 283605.0,
      "end_time": 285415.0,
      "text": "Like, in an Uber Pool."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 285439.0,
      "end_time": 286485.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 286509.0,
      "end_time": 289120.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, I noticed you looking at my feet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 289144.0,
      "end_time": 293310.0,
      "text": "\"What? Dude, no, I&#39;m just making slides. I&#39;m a consultant. I make slides."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 293334.0,
      "end_time": 295684.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m making PowerPoint slides, I&#39;m not looking --\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 295708.0,
      "end_time": 296876.0,
      "text": "\"No, it&#39;s fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 296900.0,
      "end_time": 298303.0,
      "text": "I get why you&#39;d be looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298327.0,
      "end_time": 300431.0,
      "text": "The plastic on my shoe must be bothering you."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 300455.0,
      "end_time": 302983.0,
      "text": "Well, let me talk about it for the rest of this ride."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 303700.0,
      "end_time": 305417.0,
      "text": "You see, the plastic on my shoe is from the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 305441.0,
      "end_time": 307592.0,
      "text": "on my feet, not in your fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 307616.0,
      "end_time": 309772.0,
      "text": "being walked on, not being munched on."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 309796.0,
      "end_time": 312319.0,
      "text": "Happy feet. Happy fish. Happy ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 312343.0,
      "end_time": 314686.0,
      "text": "Doing my part. I got eco-shoes. I got eco-shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 314710.0,
      "end_time": 316539.0,
      "text": "You need some eco-shoes?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 316563.0,
      "end_time": 319270.0,
      "text": "And so on, just cornering him. We&#39;ve all been there."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 319510.0,
      "end_time": 321925.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, pass me your cell phone. I&#39;ll give you a discount code."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 321949.0,
      "end_time": 323556.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a discount code.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 323580.0,
      "end_time": 324731.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all been --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 324755.0,
      "end_time": 326903.0,
      "text": "Folks, I have jumped out of moving Uber Pools."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 326927.0,
      "end_time": 328320.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 328560.0,
      "end_time": 330678.0,
      "text": "Just, moving, highway, I&#39;m out. I&#39;m out."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 332567.0,
      "end_time": 335854.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve got to forgive the hipsters, we need to love the hipsters."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 335878.0,
      "end_time": 338366.0,
      "text": "We need hipsters, and we need companies like Adidas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 338391.0,
      "end_time": 341891.0,
      "text": "and what we need most is for investors to convince other companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 341915.0,
      "end_time": 343527.0,
      "text": "to behave like Adidas."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 343551.0,
      "end_time": 345258.0,
      "text": "And herein lies the challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 345969.0,
      "end_time": 349863.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a growing group of investors, call them \"conscious investors.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 349887.0,
      "end_time": 352657.0,
      "text": "Conscious investors care about ESG issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 353791.0,
      "end_time": 357978.0,
      "text": "And they talk a lot about engaging management on ESG issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 358200.0,
      "end_time": 360647.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t actually get management to make changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 360671.0,
      "end_time": 363455.0,
      "text": "that will improve the environment and society."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 364780.0,
      "end_time": 367654.0,
      "text": "And this is where conscious investors can take a page from the playbook"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 367678.0,
      "end_time": 369609.0,
      "text": "of the activist investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 369633.0,
      "end_time": 373549.0,
      "text": "because the activist investors have no issues getting management to make changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 373574.0,
      "end_time": 376100.0,
      "text": "They have no issues turning up the heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 376124.0,
      "end_time": 377322.0,
      "text": "Take Paul Singer."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 377346.0,
      "end_time": 379689.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s an old-school Wall Street OG,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 379713.0,
      "end_time": 383421.0,
      "text": "now in his 70s, loves Doritos, loves making money."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 384474.0,
      "end_time": 387881.0,
      "text": "Argentina owed Paul 600 million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 387905.0,
      "end_time": 389816.0,
      "text": "and would not pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 390386.0,
      "end_time": 391552.0,
      "text": "Big mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 391576.0,
      "end_time": 394987.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t take money from an OG and not pay it back."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 395425.0,
      "end_time": 397872.0,
      "text": "Paul went to war with Argentina."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 397896.0,
      "end_time": 399990.0,
      "text": "I am not inventing."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 400140.0,
      "end_time": 401583.0,
      "text": "This is big. This was huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 401607.0,
      "end_time": 404246.0,
      "text": "This was bigger than Tyson vs Holyfield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 404270.0,
      "end_time": 405637.0,
      "text": "Ali vs Foreman."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 405661.0,
      "end_time": 407702.0,
      "text": "This was man vs country."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 407726.0,
      "end_time": 412473.0,
      "text": "Paul Singer started going around the world trying to seize up Argentinian assets."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 412497.0,
      "end_time": 417162.0,
      "text": "At one point, he tried to seize an Argentinian navy vessel"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 417186.0,
      "end_time": 418440.0,
      "text": "off the coast of Ghana."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 418464.0,
      "end_time": 421900.0,
      "text": "He tried to take over a 350-foot ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 421924.0,
      "end_time": 425842.0,
      "text": "while big navy officers with big guns were on the ship."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 425866.0,
      "end_time": 429400.0,
      "text": "He got the police in Ghana to show up with a crane"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 429424.0,
      "end_time": 430902.0,
      "text": "and threaten to board the ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 430927.0,
      "end_time": 435439.0,
      "text": "and it wasn&#39;t until the navy officers drew their weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 435463.0,
      "end_time": 437270.0,
      "text": "that they called off the operation."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 437770.0,
      "end_time": 440358.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I call turning up the heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 440382.0,
      "end_time": 441599.0,
      "text": "Now, you may say"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 442479.0,
      "end_time": 444772.0,
      "text": "Paul lost the battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 444797.0,
      "end_time": 446368.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll say, Paul won the war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 446392.0,
      "end_time": 448232.0,
      "text": "because Paul didn&#39;t get paid one time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 448256.0,
      "end_time": 451380.0,
      "text": "he got paid 20 times his original investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 452831.0,
      "end_time": 454353.0,
      "text": "Then you have Barry Rosenstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 454377.0,
      "end_time": 455666.0,
      "text": "His fund, Jana Partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 455690.0,
      "end_time": 458145.0,
      "text": "started stealth-mode buying up stock in Whole Foods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 458169.0,
      "end_time": 460572.0,
      "text": "at a time when Whole Foods was struggling."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 460596.0,
      "end_time": 462496.0,
      "text": "They got to eight percent, came out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 462520.0,
      "end_time": 465275.0,
      "text": "and pushed Whole Foods to sell itself to Amazon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 465300.0,
      "end_time": 469349.0,
      "text": "and not because Barry wanted same-day delivery of his organic Doritos."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 469373.0,
      "end_time": 470404.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 470998.0,
      "end_time": 472984.0,
      "text": "He wanted to make some money."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 473800.0,
      "end_time": 475798.0,
      "text": "Now, the CEO of Whole Foods, John Mackey, and the board"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 475822.0,
      "end_time": 480300.0,
      "text": "did not want to sell themselves to Amazon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 480540.0,
      "end_time": 482746.0,
      "text": "because that would be the prime example of selling out."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 483275.0,
      "end_time": 485352.0,
      "text": "But in the end, they caved."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 485879.0,
      "end_time": 488457.0,
      "text": "Why? Because Barry turned up the heat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 488481.0,
      "end_time": 491328.0,
      "text": "and he made 300 million dollars in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 491777.0,
      "end_time": 494885.0,
      "text": "And he did not leave a very nice impression on John."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 495605.0,
      "end_time": 498363.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not going to see John and Barry just hugging it out"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 498387.0,
      "end_time": 499658.0,
      "text": "at the Whole Foods caf√©."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 500765.0,
      "end_time": 502765.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a very different example now:"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 503524.0,
      "end_time": 506200.0,
      "text": "the Chicago Teachers&#39; Pension Fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 506829.0,
      "end_time": 509358.0,
      "text": "a $10 billion conscious investor."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 509915.0,
      "end_time": 512846.0,
      "text": "They recently came out hard against private prisons in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 512870.0,
      "end_time": 514235.0,
      "text": "and good for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 514259.0,
      "end_time": 517324.0,
      "text": "As a new parent, I tell you, I am troubled by devastating images"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 517347.0,
      "end_time": 520852.0,
      "text": "of young children being ripped out of the arms of their parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 520876.0,
      "end_time": 522600.0,
      "text": "at the US border"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 522850.0,
      "end_time": 525571.0,
      "text": "and being placed in private detention facilities that did too little"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 525595.0,
      "end_time": 528752.0,
      "text": "to help the kids maintain contact with their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 529600.0,
      "end_time": 531360.0,
      "text": "So what did the Chicago teachers do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 532459.0,
      "end_time": 535255.0,
      "text": "Did they get management to make changes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 535279.0,
      "end_time": 536544.0,
      "text": "Did they turn up the heat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 536568.0,
      "end_time": 538687.0,
      "text": "Did they look management in the eye and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 538711.0,
      "end_time": 540389.0,
      "text": "\"This is no way to run a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 541440.0,
      "end_time": 543669.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a different way to do things. Let me show you\"?"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 543693.0,
      "end_time": 547122.0,
      "text": "No. They just sold their stock."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 547972.0,
      "end_time": 549428.0,
      "text": "Selling did nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 549452.0,
      "end_time": 551829.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not like management woke up the next day"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 551853.0,
      "end_time": 553305.0,
      "text": "and had an epiphany and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 553330.0,
      "end_time": 556826.0,
      "text": "\"Gosh, the teachers sold their stock. We&#39;d better be nice to the kids.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 556850.0,
      "end_time": 558262.0,
      "text": "No. That didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 558971.0,
      "end_time": 562952.0,
      "text": "And despite a decade of several high-profile divestitures"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 562976.0,
      "end_time": 564760.0,
      "text": "in private prison stock in the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 564784.0,
      "end_time": 566489.0,
      "text": "the stock has continued to climb."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 566513.0,
      "end_time": 570600.0,
      "text": "The stock over that same period has outperformed the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 571941.0,
      "end_time": 573197.0,
      "text": "And the biggest issue is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 573221.0,
      "end_time": 576818.0,
      "text": "we went from a set of conscious investors owning the stock"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 576842.0,
      "end_time": 581608.0,
      "text": "to it potentially being owned by investors who don&#39;t care about these issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 581632.0,
      "end_time": 583954.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t care what you think about these issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 584423.0,
      "end_time": 586994.0,
      "text": "And this is my issue with conscious investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 587180.0,
      "end_time": 589151.0,
      "text": "Their MO is to divest"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 589175.0,
      "end_time": 591824.0,
      "text": "or divert money into ESG-focused funds."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 592887.0,
      "end_time": 596189.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t divest your way to a greener world."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 597261.0,
      "end_time": 599579.0,
      "text": "You can divest your way to a greener portfolio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 599603.0,
      "end_time": 601222.0,
      "text": "not to a greener world."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 602722.0,
      "end_time": 604550.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s it going to take?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 604790.0,
      "end_time": 606130.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s it going to take to flip the script,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 606154.0,
      "end_time": 609600.0,
      "text": "to get conscious investors to go from divesting to engaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 609300.0,
      "end_time": 612507.0,
      "text": "to go from talking about engaging to actually working with management"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 612532.0,
      "end_time": 616557.0,
      "text": "to make changes that will improve their ESG performance?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 617478.0,
      "end_time": 620376.0,
      "text": "Because there&#39;s a lot suggesting they should and they could."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 620400.0,
      "end_time": 623473.0,
      "text": "They should, given the clear correlation between ESG performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 623497.0,
      "end_time": 624921.0,
      "text": "and financial performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 625877.0,
      "end_time": 628712.0,
      "text": "They could because the activists have shown us they could."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 629529.0,
      "end_time": 631693.0,
      "text": "A shareholder can drive change in a company."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 631717.0,
      "end_time": 635646.0,
      "text": "The difference is, Paul and Barry do what they do to make money."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 636433.0,
      "end_time": 641532.0,
      "text": "The conscious investors would do it to improve society and the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 641556.0,
      "end_time": 643309.0,
      "text": "and make money in the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 643333.0,
      "end_time": 646329.0,
      "text": "and do it a little more collaboratively and constructively."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 647245.0,
      "end_time": 650250.0,
      "text": "And they have the backing of the some of the largest investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 650274.0,
      "end_time": 653263.0,
      "text": "Vanguard and BlackRock -- together, they manage trillions."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 653287.0,
      "end_time": 656699.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been increasingly vocal about the importance of ESG."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 657542.0,
      "end_time": 661526.0,
      "text": "The CEO of BlackRock has been increasingly vocal in his annual letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 661550.0,
      "end_time": 662881.0,
      "text": "about this issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 663512.0,
      "end_time": 668281.0,
      "text": "Even Jana Partners, the same OGs that John called \"greedy bastards,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 668306.0,
      "end_time": 670971.0,
      "text": "recently co-wrote an open letter to the board of Apple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 670995.0,
      "end_time": 674122.0,
      "text": "saying, \"Hey, your smartphones are addictive for children."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 674969.0,
      "end_time": 676165.0,
      "text": "Fix it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 676813.0,
      "end_time": 678467.0,
      "text": "Apple is working on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 679983.0,
      "end_time": 682204.0,
      "text": "So what it&#39;s going to take is some pressure."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 682744.0,
      "end_time": 685349.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to take some pressure on conscious investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 685373.0,
      "end_time": 688200.0,
      "text": "to, in turn, put some pressure on management"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 688224.0,
      "end_time": 692477.0,
      "text": "to make changes that will improve the environment and society."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 693520.0,
      "end_time": 694675.0,
      "text": "And where do they start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 694700.0,
      "end_time": 697511.0,
      "text": "They start by picking an issue that matters to them"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 697535.0,
      "end_time": 698837.0,
      "text": "and taking a stand on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 699376.0,
      "end_time": 702631.0,
      "text": "Take a stand on an issue that lines up with your purpose:"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 703313.0,
      "end_time": 705958.0,
      "text": "water preservation, labor rights, diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 705982.0,
      "end_time": 708819.0,
      "text": "As long as it lines up with your purpose, you are golden."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 709393.0,
      "end_time": 711280.0,
      "text": "And the biggest unlock?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 711520.0,
      "end_time": 716190.0,
      "text": "Get the senior-most investment professionals focused on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 716590.0,
      "end_time": 718868.0,
      "text": "Today, when an activist shows up to a campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 718892.0,
      "end_time": 722351.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the senior investment professional talking to the CEO and the board"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 722375.0,
      "end_time": 723825.0,
      "text": "and everyone hears about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 723849.0,
      "end_time": 727396.0,
      "text": "When a conscious investor shows up to talk about an ESG issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 727420.0,
      "end_time": 729861.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s some junior person in the risk department"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 729885.0,
      "end_time": 733550.0,
      "text": "talking to some junior person in the investor relations department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 733790.0,
      "end_time": 735632.0,
      "text": "and nobody hears about it, and that needs to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 735657.0,
      "end_time": 737290.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not some massive leap."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 737314.0,
      "end_time": 739685.0,
      "text": "Today, when a company underperforms financially,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 739709.0,
      "end_time": 740877.0,
      "text": "who is on the hook?"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 740901.0,
      "end_time": 742570.0,
      "text": "The senior investment professional."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 742595.0,
      "end_time": 743753.0,
      "text": "So what do they do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 743777.0,
      "end_time": 745982.0,
      "text": "They drop everything and work with management,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 746600.0,
      "end_time": 747718.0,
      "text": "collaboratively and constructively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 747742.0,
      "end_time": 751246.0,
      "text": "to make changes to improve the company&#39;s financial performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 751270.0,
      "end_time": 754935.0,
      "text": "The same should be true when the company underperforms on ESG issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 754959.0,
      "end_time": 758697.0,
      "text": "And yes, that requires standardization on how we measure ESG,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 758721.0,
      "end_time": 759907.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 761201.0,
      "end_time": 763143.0,
      "text": "So folks, here&#39;s my call to action:"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 763766.0,
      "end_time": 765338.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s your money."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 765362.0,
      "end_time": 766871.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s your pension fund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 766895.0,
      "end_time": 768723.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s your sovereign wealth fund."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 768748.0,
      "end_time": 770395.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s your university&#39;s endowment."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 770419.0,
      "end_time": 771771.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s your money."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 771795.0,
      "end_time": 775439.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s your right to have your money managed in line with your values."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 775910.0,
      "end_time": 777190.0,
      "text": "So use your voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 777803.0,
      "end_time": 779318.0,
      "text": "and trust that it matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 779902.0,
      "end_time": 783735.0,
      "text": "It was your voice that got the investors more conscious in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 783759.0,
      "end_time": 785684.0,
      "text": "You protested for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 785708.0,
      "end_time": 788634.0,
      "text": "because you didn&#39;t feel right about your money being invested"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 788658.0,
      "end_time": 791442.0,
      "text": "in companies whose values don&#39;t line up with yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 791466.0,
      "end_time": 793349.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s time to use that voice again."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 793373.0,
      "end_time": 795691.0,
      "text": "But this time, instead of pushing them to divest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 795715.0,
      "end_time": 799249.0,
      "text": "push them to engage, truly engage, truly work with management"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 799273.0,
      "end_time": 802882.0,
      "text": "to make changes that will improve their ESG performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 804449.0,
      "end_time": 806524.0,
      "text": "You made them aware of the issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 806548.0,
      "end_time": 808476.0,
      "text": "You can now focus them on fixing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 809740.0,
      "end_time": 810637.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 810661.0,
      "end_time": 813400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}